srcPsmKey: string: the current PSM chainlog key
dstPsmKey: string: the new PSM chainlog key (must be != srcPsmKey)
dstPocketKey: string: the PSM pocket chainlog key
psmMomKey: string: the PSM Mom chainlog key
buf: number: the amount of Dai to premint (in Dai)
tin: number: the toll in for swaps
tout: number: the toll out for swaps
maxLine: number: the max debt ceiling (in Dai)
gap: number: the max debt ceiling adjustment (in Dai)
ttl: number: the debt ceiling adjustment cool-off (in seconds)
